                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a01"/>夫四葙無常。三<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">有</unclear>□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">邃</unclear>□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a02"/>故須<note n="0211001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02793;＝彌【中研院】</note><app n="0211001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02793;</rdg></app>至高。為劫火焰熾。□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a03"/>海淵深。為七日乾<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">竭</unclear>。況閻
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a04"/>浮形<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">像</unclear>。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">理</unclear>在難固。竊見□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a05"/>城南面有故塔一<note n="0211002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00100;＝區【中研院】</note><app n="0211002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00100;</rdg></app>。基□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a06"/>損壞。窗戶崩<note n="0211003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04130;＝缺【中研院】</note><app n="0211003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">缺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04130;</rdg></app>。塼石分□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a07"/>而信心<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">哲</unclear>人嚴<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">桃</unclear>校歎□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a08"/>圖之狼藉。□靈塔之<note n="0211004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31019;＝敗【中研院】</note><app n="0211004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">敗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31019;</rdg></app>□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a09"/>故率宗眷援及四<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">有</unclear>。鄉□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a10"/>異人。同心共脩此善樂。□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a11"/>聖容內<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">外</unclear>俱就。藉茲微□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a12"/>上為　皇帝。下及含氣□
                         <lb ed="I" n="0211a13"/>見眷屬。一時成佛。
